texting.txt.content:
Remember olds phones and how you had to type things out on a keypad?
Like how, for example, the word Yes you would have to write 999337777?
A lot of keypads don't have those keys anymore, so I've added them here for reference.
2 - A B C
3 - D E F
4 - G H I
5 - J K L
6 - M N O
7 - P Q R S
8 - T U V
9 - W X Y Z
